Author: ca333#0118
Content:
@CHMEX thanks for the efforts anyway. yes - i think its better to wait a little bit since we just got started. i am not going to engage community wise and prefer to stay in the background. 
The volume does not meet the listing requirement neither. CMC stated to me some long time ago that the source of trading-volume also plays a big role. My plan is to wait at least a week till we have regular volume on barterDEX and then apply while the hackathon campaign is ongoing.
